        "timestamp": 1735770091
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>What do you mean exactly? Each of the three questions comes with two options (implication followed by non-implication). Maybe it's not displayed correctly on mobile?<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/7cU9FSQVvrl8e0iPrXg1SCOI/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/7cU9FSQVvrl8e0iPrXg1SCOI/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"770x252\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/7cU9FSQVvrl8e0iPrXg1SCOI/image.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
