    {
        "content": "<p>It looks like it might get displayed as the following in some fonts (could be tiny)<br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/xe3H047bBYAETepRK_OxGf0f/image.png\">image.png</a><br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/w5f1IoqoSveutND_XHRjwTKk/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/xe3H047bBYAETepRK_OxGf0f/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"47x47\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/xe3H047bBYAETepRK_OxGf0f/image.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/w5f1IoqoSveutND_XHRjwTKk/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img data-original-dimensions=\"34x31\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/w5f1IoqoSveutND_XHRjwTKk/image.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
